name: Peace Coker
description: As far as games, I am tired of those, as well. It is so ridiculous to me. If you are interested in someone, just tell them. If you aren’t, just tell them. We are adults and should be able to handle these things! I cannot understand why women and men play such childish games. And if you can’t already tell, I’m not into drama! LOL!! I don’t like to argue and I’m not high maintenance. Like i say , I don’t like arguing or yelling, that gets neither person anywhere.. ! Also i love to cook, and have been told I’m good at it…Italian, Thai, Cajun/Creole…from grilling to gourmet, including pies, cakes and bread from scratch
